{"tid":995471,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)猛火爆1-2 不死劫 思·裂","createTime":"2019-01-25T12:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T19:26:21.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6c5046bb60476ecdaa635173bfc296601e32c9c8","tid":995471,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T12:31:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=2zg5K6sz%2BK3wx%2BOtRjj9UHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d19e4f9f\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=2zg5K6sz%2BK3wx%2BOtRjj9UHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=47a10206\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=2zg5K6sz%2BK3wx%2BOtRjj9UHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=2a9a199b\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/c4/%E7%8C%9B%E7%81%AB%E7%88%86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fc4%2F%25E7%258C%259B%25E7%2581%25AB%25E7%2588%2586.jpg&h=946b05f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9e/RED_2_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9e%2FRED_2_poster.jpg&h=3c316e90&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/7d/Unbreakable_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F7d%2FUnbreakable_Poster.jpg&h=cbfa23a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/df/Split_2017_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fdf%2FSplit_2017_Poster.jpg&h=3a133ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.法蘭克莫西斯（Frank Moses；布魯斯&middot;威利飾演）是一名自CIA退休的前特工，被CIA的分類為RED，即為已退休而極度危險的（Retired, Extremely Dangerous），他感到退休生活十分無趣沒有變化，唯一的樂趣是每月撕毀養老金支票藉故與養老金管理人莎拉羅斯（Sarah Ross；瑪莉&middot;露易絲&middot;派克飾演）在電話裡的談天說地時間，且法蘭克對莎拉在心中漸生情愫；一日法蘭克家中突然闖入了數名傭兵，想要將法蘭克滅口，法蘭克憑著過去的矯健身手將傭兵團擊退後，發現攻擊的背後有著巨大的陰謀存在；因此為了保護所愛的人，法蘭克決定召集過去的老戰友們，來對抗陰謀的幕後黑手並揭發真相&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n2.出生入死、爾虞我詐的諜報世界裡，你要相信薑是老的辣！退而不休，寶刀未老的探員法蘭克（布魯斯威利 飾）憑著往昔經驗和過人能耐，將與他的昔日戰友再度出手，不但要拯救世界免於核子威脅，更要保全他們自己的老命...<br />\n<br />\n3.故事敘述在費城，擔任體育場保安的大衛&middot;杜恩在一場列車失事下倖存，成為了唯一倖存者。此時，他遇見了從一出生就患有成骨不全症的漫畫藝術收藏家伊利亞&middot;普林斯，從小他就相當容易骨折。伊利亞對大衛感到相當有興趣，這使得大衛在處理自己家庭糾紛的同時，也開始對自己的身體展開疑惑，並打算藉由調查來了解自己為何與眾不同，這似乎與伊利亞有著密切的關連<br />\n<br />\n4.故事敘述凱文被信任的心理醫生診斷出擁有二十三個人格，但還有一個未知人格尚未覺醒。在眾多人格的競爭下，這也造成他動身綁架了三名十幾歲的少女，以醞釀未知的計劃....<br />\n<br />\n8 40PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=2zg5K6sz%2BK3wx%2BOtRjj9UHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=344f0293\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=2zg5K6sz%2BK3wx%2BOtRjj9UHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=8276782e\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd79b096283570d3066603ac0bc8abbc31c2a43d","tid":995471,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T12:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-q7mHKHApRZM/WeTJENrM0JI/AAAAAAAACZ8/EGJ6AeSZugg2XfASnnCGeigP-DPReitngCLcBGAs/s1600/split.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-q7mHKHApRZM%2FWeTJENrM0JI%2FAAAAAAAACZ8%2FEGJ6AeSZugg2XfASnnCGeigP-DPReitngCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2Fsplit.jpeg&h=c9c1124c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3ff456420a978791bee831189331f4af5996a08","tid":995471,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T12:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0fa2dbc749d30ab72dbaf9dbbe037e58148bdc","tid":995471,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T13:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e516d373c752c924c50d3ab9042ba7306665ad","tid":995471,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T15:11:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd9a1abf4ca0b7de211da4a85f1a66d68f91d1d","tid":995471,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T15:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2931bf033b4d85fea0545ee3fb9572e518ec7c30","tid":995471,"uid":29160,"li